ğŸ—“ï¸ 1. India Blockchain Month
India Blockchain Month (INBM) is a month-long celebration of Web3 and blockchain technology across India.
It features meetups, workshops, hackathons, conferences, and community events in many cities.
In 2025, India Blockchain Month is scheduled around September (with significant flagship events in late September). (indiablockchainmonth.com)
Key points:
Celebrated over an entire month
Brings together developers, builders, investors, policymakers
Includes events in 20+ cities across India (indiablockchainmonth.com)

