ğŸ“Œ Summary  
India Blockchain Month: Held annually around September, a month-long festival of blockchain learning and innovation across multiple cities in India. (indiablockchainmonth.com)
India Blockchain Week: Held annually in December, a focused 7-day celebration of blockchain and Web3 events, mainly in Bengaluru. (India Blockchain Week Conference)

 

